column2: SELECT g.objid, g.specobjid, sp.specobjid, sp.plate, sp.mjd, sp.fiberid, sp.z as redshift, sp.zErr as redshift_err, sp.z_noqso, sp.zErr_noqso, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp, sp.veldisperr as sp_vdisp_err FROM SpecObj AS sp JOIN Galaxy AS g ON sp.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE (sp.plate = # and sp.mjd = # and sp.fiberid = #)
